metadata.title: DPM, UK High Commissioner discuss cooperation at multilateral fora

content.article_body: ISLAMABAD, Jun 11 (APP):UK High Commissioner, Jane Marriott called on Deputy Prime Minister/Foreign Minister (DPM/FM), Senator Mohammad Ishaq Dar here and discussed bilateral cooperation at the multilateral fora, particularly at the UN Security Council. During the meeting, both the dignitaries exchanged views on Pak-UK bilateral relations, regional and global issues of mutual interest, a DPM's Office news release said.
